  <h2>1) DNS & TLS</h2>
  <ul><li>A-record: <code>voice.quirkcars.com → public IP (on-prem)</code>. Let’s Encrypt via Caddy.</li></ul>

  <h2>2) Caddy</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>WS endpoint: <code>/realtime/twilio</code>, forward to OpenAI Realtime with API key.</li>
    <li>Access logs enabled; redact as needed.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>3) Twilio number</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Voice → TwiML Bin (pilot) with WebSocket connect to Caddy endpoint.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>4) Verify</h2>
  <ul><li>Call flow and logs; confirm audio round-trip and agent responses.</li></ul>

